# Beach Scoring System Flow

## Region Filter Click Flow

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[User Clicks Region in RegionFilter Component] --> B[handleRegionClick Called]
    B --> C[dispatch changeRegion Thunk]
    
    C --> D1[Set Selected Region]
    C --> D2[Find Region Object]
    
    D2 --> E1[Fetch Beaches by Region ID]
    D2 --> E2[Fetch Forecast Data]
    
    E1 --> F[Wait for Both Fetches]
    E2 --> F
    
    F --> G[dispatch calculateBeachScores Thunk]
    
    G --> H[Get Current State]
    H --> I[Validate Data]
    I --> J[Format Forecast Data]
    
    J --> K[Filter Beaches by Region]
    K --> L[Calculate Score for Each Beach]
    L --> M[Create Score Map]
    
    M --> N[Update Redux Store]
    N --> O[Update UI Components]
    
    subgraph Score Calculation
        L --> L1[Check Wind Direction]
        L --> L2[Check Wave Size]
        L --> L3[Check Swell Direction]
        L --> L4[Check Swell Period]
        L1 & L2 & L3 & L4 --> L5[Calculate Final Score]
    end
```

